Title: The Horse Dancer
Description: When financial troubles threaten to shut down a girls horse camp, one of America's most promising young gymnasts, Samantha Wick, uses her gymnastic prowess to start a horse-dancing team to raise money and save the day.

Title: Godha
Description: Captain, a former wrestler, sends his son Das to Punjab for higher studies. Once there, Das falls in love with Aditi, a champion wrestler, who inspires him to pursue the sport.

Title: Gold
Description: The journey of a man who was instrumental in making India win its first Olympic gold medal as a free nation.
